.reviews__response-cover.reviews__response-cover-success 
    .reviews__response.reviews__modal-success 
        .reviews__modal-wr-close
            .reviews__modal-close
        .reviews__response-icon.reviews__response-icon_succ
        .reviews__modal-text 
            p Ваш отзыв успешно отправлен

